1455
01:26:13,875 --> 01:26:16,167
- Hey.
- Hi.

1456
01:26:16,250 --> 01:26:17,125
Andi.

1457
01:26:18,375 --> 01:26:19,333
Yes.

1458
01:26:19,417 --> 01:26:21,833
